children.name: The LR01 uses the same design as the most iconic bikes from PEUGEOT Cycles' 130-year history and combines it with agile, dynamic performance that's perfectly suited to navigating today's cities. As well as a lugged steel frame and iconic PEUGEOT black-and-white chequer design, this city bike also features a 16-speed Shimano Claris drivetrain.
